  "prompt": "Which is the best institute in Mumbai for big data analytics with the best placement?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, several institutes in Mumbai are renowned for their Big Data Analytics programs and have good placement records. Among them are:\n\n1. **SP Jain Institute of Management and Research (SPJIMR)**: Known for its robust curriculum and strong industry connections, SPJIMR offers excellent placement opportunities.\n  \n2. **Narsee Monjee Institute of Management Studies (NMIMS)**: NMIMS provides a comprehensive program in Big Data Analytics and has a strong placement cell that ensures good job opportunities for its graduates.\n\n3. **Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Bombay**: IIT Bombay offers specialized courses in data analytics and has one of the best placement records in the country.\n\n4. **Mumbai University \u2013 Department of Computer Science**: Offers specialized courses and has collaborations with various industries for placement.\n\n5. **Great Lakes Institute of Management**: Known for its Post Graduate Program in Business Analytics and Business Intelligence, Great Lakes has a good placement track record.\n\nTo determine the best institute for you, consider factors such as the specific course curriculum, faculty expertise, industry connections, and alumni feedback. It is also beneficial to reach out to current students or alumni to get firsthand insights into the placement support and opportunities provided.",
